[In the midst of the current influenza epidemic in Greece some sudden
deaths from influenza are to be expected, but the medica authorities
apparently suspect these cases to be viral meningitis. Since it is not the
mosquito season there, West Nile viral meningitis can be ruled out. - Mod.JW]
